race.comment: MEPUNGA LARA (4) recorded her Best Time this course and distance when a 42.86 winner of a Grade 4/5 in one of the quickest wins on the program. Should be in this for a long way. GREYSYND SAMMY (3) was well supported last time but could only manage second (36.87), beaten 3 lengths. Has won two of three starts from this draw. Leading player again. SWEET SUNDOWN (2) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 2 lengths away in second (34.78) at this track in a Special conditions H over 600m. Must be included in calculations. MAGIC SNOWDROP (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.
